# ============================================
# Netlify Ignore File - JudgeFinder Platform
# ============================================
# Files and directories to exclude from Netlify deployment
# This prevents sensitive files and build artifacts from being uploaded
# Documentation: https://docs.netlify.com/configure-builds/file-based-configuration/#ignore-builds
